NOTE ON DERIVED DATA: The Layer A ontology (ontology/) is derived from the
HumSet dataset and the DEEP humanitarian analytical framework (Data Friendly Space /
The DEEP). Consult the HumSet dataset terms for any restrictions on the underlying
taxonomy and excerpts before redistribution. If you use the ontology in published
work, please cite HumSet (Fekih et al., 2022) — full citation in references/SOURCES.md
and CITATION.cff.
